OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,FAn 84-year-old grandmother from
OL,7,FBridgend waited more than 30 hours for
OL,8,Fan ambulance that never came after
OL,9,Ffalling and breaking her hip over the
OL,10,Fweekend.
OL,12,FMeryl Coates endured the wait while in
OL,13,Fsignificant pain and unable to sleep,
OL,14,Fonly to be told that there were no
OL,15,Fambulances available, and eventually
OL,16,Fhad to be transported to hospital by
OL,17,Fher family.
OL,19,FMeryl had called her son Andrew on
OL,20,FSaturday morning to tell him she had
OL,21,Ffallen and wasn't able to get up.
