OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,FWhen Andrew arrived at his mother's
OL,7,Fhouse, he realised he wasn't able to
OL,8,Fmove or carry her to his car as she
OL,9,Fwas in so much pain.
OL,11,FHe called an ambulance just before
OL,12,F10:30AM on Saturday, but by Sunday
OL,13,Fafternoon, one still hadn't arrived.
OL,15,F"We hear stories in the press of
OL,16,Fpeople lying on the ground for 8, 10,
OL,17,Fhours, so we expected an 8 hour wait.
OL,19,F"But I had no idea it was going to be
OL,20,Fthat long," Andrew Coates said.
