OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,F"I made several (999) calls over the
OL,7,Fperiod. They called me a few times as
OL,8,Fwell. And finally, my last phone call
OL,9,Fwas 29 hours after my initial call."
OL,11,FMeryl was initially instructed not to
OL,12,Fhave any food, water or pain
OL,13,Fmedication until an ambulance had
OL,14,Farrived.
OL,16,FOnly after a wait of 21 hours was
OL,17,FAndrew advised that Meryl could have
OL,18,Fsomething to eat and drink, along with
OL,19,Fsome pain medication.
