OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,FEventually Andrew gave up waiting and
OL,7,Fdrove Meryl to hospital himself, which
OL,8,Finvolved lifting her into his car
OL,9,Fdespite her having a suspected broken
OL,10,Fhip.
OL,12,FBut Andrew said it was a decision he
OL,13,Ffelt forced into making,
OL,15,F"There was no indication if we would
OL,16,Fget (the ambulance) that day or not.
OL,18,F"It was, 'You're almost at the top of
OL,19,Fthe list.' But there was no indication
OL,20,Fif there was light at the end of the
OL,21,Ftunnel."
