OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,F"Obviously you understand that if
OL,7,Fpeople ring up with a heart attack or
OL,8,Fa broken leg, the heart attack is
OL,9,Fgoing to be first.
OL,11,F"But 30 hours is pushing it way beyond
OL,12,Fthe extreme. It was really, really
OL,13,Ffrustrating."
OL,15,FSonia Thompson, Assistant Director of
OL,16,FOperations at the Welsh Ambulance
OL,17,FService, said the service is "deeply
OL,18,Fsorry" for the family's experience,
OL,19,Fsaying: "This is not the level of
OL,20,Fservice we wish to provide to
OL,21,Fpatients."
