OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,FShe added that the service is under
OL,7,F"extreme and well-documented pressure
OL,8,Fas a result of wider system pressures
OL,9,Facross the NHS," compounded this
OL,10,Fweekend by Storm Bert.
OL,12,FThe statement continued: "As an
OL,13,Fambulance service, we're thinking very
OL,14,Fdifferently about the way we deliver
OL,15,Fservices in future, and we are already
OL,16,Ftesting some new ways of working to
OL,17,Funderstand how we can relieve some of
OL,18,Fthe pressure in the system while
OL,19,Fcontinuing to provide patients with
OL,20,Fthe care they need."
