OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,FAndrew said the lack of pain relief
OL,7,Ffor Meryl was one of the most
OL,8,Fdifficult parts of her ordeal.
OL,10,F"Even if you just get somebody around
OL,11,F(the house) to give some pain relief,
OL,12,Fexplaining, 'You can't be taken into
OL,13,Fhospital, but we can make it more
OL,14,Fcomfortable, give you some pain
OL,15,Frelief, and hopefully ambulance will
OL,16,Fbe around soon to deal with it
OL,17,Fproperly,'" Andrew said.
