OL,3,CGran, 84, waited 30 hours with broken
OL,4,Chip for ambulance that never came
OL,6,FIt comes as the Health Secretary
OL,7,FJeremy Miles today announced a review
OL,8,Finto targets for ambulance response
OL,9,Ftimes as recommended by the Senedd's
OL,10,Fhealth committee.
OL,12,FCurrently 65% of the most serious
OL,13,Fcalls should be answered within 8
OL,14,Fminutes, but that target hasn't been
OL,15,Fmet in over 4 years.
OL,17,F"Targets have to be realistic... But
OL,18,Fif there's a target for a reason, then
OL,19,Fyou have to have the resources,"
OL,20,FAndrew said, who believes it is a
OL,21,F"whole-system problem."
