OL,6,FThe review will conclude at the end of
OL,7,Fnext February.
OL,9,FResponding to the review, Sam Rowlands
OL,10,FMS, Welsh Conservative Shadow Health
OL,11,FMinister said: "We need bold action
OL,12,Ffrom the Labour Welsh Government to
OL,13,Freduce ambulance waits, not just a
OL,14,Freview of the targets.
OL,16,F"Barely half of the most serious
OL,17,Fambulance calls receive a response
OL,18,Fwithin the target time. We need clear
OL,19,Fand transparent targets to improve
OL,20,Faccountability.
