OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives want to see a
OL,7,Flong-term plan, involving social care,
OL,8,Fto address capacity issues within the
OL,9,FWelsh NHS to improve the flow of
OL,10,Fpatients into and out of hospitals
OL,11,Fthat applies pragmatic, cross-sector
OL,12,Fthinking and makes use of cross-border
OL,13,Favailability."
